name: PIXEL EYES #1
description: Music and visual arts have always been the fuel of my life. And now I am making available exclusive works at Hic Et Nunc, which are part of the personal collection. The instrumental was produced in the MK1 maschine, and the visuals were manipulated in image and vector programs. Focus on the image and the sound. Made in Brazil.
